{"tid":502308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12歲女童廣東道唐樓單位浴室遭肢解　雙程證母親被捕","createTime":"2017-12-17T18:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T03:36:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c190b09afd0a7f8ed1f7a9828193e6a1a8741b","tid":502308,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1370573_1_20171218011416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1370573_1_20171218011416.jpg&h=156d047b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角廣東道1182號一個唐樓單位發生謀殺案，一名年約12歲女童在浴室被肢解，她的37歲持雙程證母親被捕。<br />\n<br />\n旺角警區刑事助理指揮官鍾志明表示，警方晚上10時許接報，到上址進行調查時，發現37歲疑兇在屋外，她當時並不合作，警方要破門入屋。其後在單位內的浴室發現死者，她的頭和身體已被肢解，浴室被肢體阻塞，水浸滿單位。<br />\n<br />\n鍾志明表示，案件列作謀殺案處理，正調查疑兇的行兇動機，以及死者死因，他說有關家庭並無家暴紀錄，警方亦正調查死者父親的背景。至於死者是一名持香港身份證的女童，在香港讀書。"},{"pid":"248184f9300a63bac6495a020beafb786d3077cf","tid":502308,"uid":162696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T18:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd20512a743d6288e0c94c0b09db8c032aa903c9","tid":502308,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T20:06:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94b55904cebbe4ce7dd07bccf085867674263719","tid":502308,"uid":14518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T20:06:57.000Z","msg":"咁撚癲"},{"pid":"4e55b0825a176121c3acda68e533e0decd7d72bb","tid":502308,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T20:44:11.000Z","msg":"又有鬼故"},{"pid":"932fa9356a5c8266cf0456bca1028eaa2b24c240","tid":502308,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}